C --> C2[Fix Negative Values]
C --> C3[Remove Duplicates]

C --> D[Feature Engineering]
D --> D1[Create total_usage]
D --> D2[Create usage_per_day]
D --> D3[Create customer_value]

D --> E[Exploratory Data Analysis]
